@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mwtmme(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.cos((v0 + 0.26 * tmp + 0.49)))
    v1 = wp.sin((0.77 - (v1 + 0.02 * v2 + 0.92)))
    v2 = (wp.exp(0.13) + (tmp + wp.exp(tmp + 0.32)))
    v0 = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.86 - v0 + 0.18)) - wp.exp(wp.sin(v2 + 0.64)))
    tmp = v0
    data[tid] = v0
